* Added support for Update 33 (Ascending Tide)
* Added Russian localization by GJSmoker

Version 1.3.7 (2021/10/10)
* Added an optional includedCharIds parameter to GetItemKnowledgeList to
  prevent specific character IDs from being excluded by the tracking filters

Version 1.3.6 (2021/10/01)
* Blacklisted item ID 126863, "Diagram: Dwarven Pipeline Cap, Sealed"

Version 1.3.5 (2021/09/28)
* Added support for Update 32 (The Deadlands)

Version 1.3.4 (2021/08/02)
* Fixed an issue where the "High" and "Low" text in the settings were changed
  as a result of ZOS changing the text associated with SI_HIGH and SI_LOW

Version 1.3.3 (2021/07/14)
* Fixed an issue where the addition of the full Ancestral Akaviri book in the
  data for Update 31 caused the style to become invalidated in Update 30

Version 1.3.2 (2021/07/14)
* Added support for Update 31 (Waking Flame)

Version 1.3.1 (2021/06/03)
* Corrected the number associated with the Thorn Legion crafting motif style

Version 1.3.0 (2021/05/20)
* Improved the encoding used by the export/import data sharing feature to be
  more space-efficient, so that more characters can be processed before
  reaching the data limit

Version 1.2.0 (2021/05/03)
* The item parameter for GetItemKnowledgeForCharacter and GetItemKnowledgeList
  has been moved to be the first parameter of both functions
* The server and charId parameters for GetItemKnowledgeForCharacter are now
  optional
* When using the style ID as an alternative item parameter, a chapter ID can
  now be optionally supplied as well

Version 1.1.0 (2021/05/02)
* The data from GetMotifItemsFromStyle now includes the motif number and a
  flag indicating whether the motif is a Crown Store exclusive
* The item parameter used by various functions can now be used to pass along a
  style ID instead

